

r.stats - 

r.stats calculates the area present in each of the @glossary("categories",16.glossary/cat.def) of
user-selected @glossary("raster",16.glossary/rastdata.def) map layer(s).  Area statistics can be given in
units of acres, hectares, square miles and @glossary("cell",16.glossary/cell.def) counts.  This
analysis uses the current @glossary("geographic region",16.glossary/georeg.def) and @glossary("mask",16.glossary/mask.def) settings.
Output can be sent to a file in the user's current working directory.

